title: Ep 10 - The Power of Belief
itunes:title: Ep 10 - The Power of Belief
description:
You can literally do anything you set your mind to.
In this episode we speak about the power of belief and knowing that you can achieve what you set your mind to. We also talk about psychological governors and self limiting beliefs that people place on themselves and how to break through them.
